    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Resting bells of Afro-Cuban origin. They are struck, and clapperless. In some locations, they are multiple bells.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
